8. Mention at what instance have you used the SSH ?

Answer: I have used SSH to log into a remote machine and work on the command line. Beside this, I have also used it to tunnel into the system in order to facilitate secure encrypted communications between two untrusted hosts over an insecure network. (Top 50 Devops Interview Questions and Answers Pdf)

9. Explain how would you handle revision (version) control ?

Answer: My approach to handle revision control would be to post the code on SourceForge or GitHub so everyone can view it. Also, I will post the checklist from the last revision to make sure that any unsolved issues are resolved.

